<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-Zenh87qX5JnK2Jl0vWa8Ck2rdkQ2Bzep5IDxbcnCeuOxjzrPF/et3URy9Bv1WTRi" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-OERcA2EqjJCMA+/3y+gxIOqMEjwtxJY7qPCqsdltbNJuaOe923+mo//f6V8Qbsw3" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    
    <div id="upper-bar">
      <div class="link" id="one"><a href="/">Cattle</a></div>
      <div class="link" id="two"><a href="/shed">Shed</a></div>
      <div class="link" id="three"><a href="/grazing">Grazing</a></div>
      <div class="link" id="four"><a href="/milk">Diary Output</a></div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <h1><%= title %></h1>
    <br>
    <br>
    <div id="text-part">
      <p>Health and welfare information of each animal is continously measured and stored to spot possible outbreaks of disease in its early stages. Fertility is strictly measured as well in order to time insemination.</p>
      <p>To check on the health and welfare of the individual animal, please provide the tag id of the respective cattle.</p>
      <br>
      <br>
      <br>
      <div>
        <form action="/grazingblocklist" method="get">
          <label for="tagId">Tag-ID</label>
          <input type="number" name="tagId">
          <button class="button" type="submit" onclick="">Add to Blocklist</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <div id="text-part">
      <br>
      <ul>
      <% if(error) { %>
        <li><%= error %></li>
      <% } else { %>
        <b>Successfully added to the blocklist</b>
        <li>Tag-ID: <%= tagId %></li>
        <li>Date Added: <%= loggedDate %></li>
        <li>Duration of no grazing: <%= timeoutLength %></li>
      </ul>
      <ul>
        <b>Full Blocklist</b>
        <% for(var i = 0; i < blocklist.length; i++) { %>
          <li><%= JSON.stringify(blocklist[i]) %></li>
        <% } %>
      </ul>
       <%= message %>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>